Description:
Tucked away.
Classic homes like this don't come to market often so make sure you get in quick. Located in an ideal spot handy to all amenities which include local schools, Corio Shopping Centre, public transport and the Princes Highway for commuters. This light and bright 3 bedroom home is sure to be a winner once inspected. Beautifully designed with a free flowing floorplan offering a range of opportunities for the first home buyer, downsizer or investors alike, you won't be disappointed. Stepping inside the home you are immediately presented with the spacious yet comfortable living area directly across from the kitchen and meals area. A central bathroom services the home with separate laundry and toilet. For those that want to entertain family and friends you can easily do so with an enormous rear yard 738m2 (approx.). Further features include ducted heating, double carport, built in robes, air conditioning and much much more. Don't miss your chance to inspect today!
Insights: 25 Hendy Street, Corio VIC 3214 was last sold in 2019 and 174 other 3 bedroom house in Corio have recently been sold.

Description:
Spacious Living & Outdoor Area
Set to the rear this two bedroom home has had a number of updates and offers spacious living both inside and outside making it a fantastic first home, investment or easy downsize option. The floor plan consists of two bedrooms, both with built in robes, a large open plan living room and dining space open to the kitchen. The generous kitchen is complete with a breakfast bar, gas stove and ample bench space looking out over the backyard. The renovated bathroom with floor to ceiling tiles, separate bath and shower services both bedrooms and has a separate toilet. Outside the large backyard wraps around the home and a single garage with remote roller door complete the property. Additional features include update flooring, external shutters and split system heating and cooling. Located a short walk from Corio Village Shopping Centre, locals schools, public transport and with easy access to the Ring Road, this property is an outstanding opportunity.
Due Diligence checklist are available at www.consumer.vic.gov.au/duediligencechecklist

Description:
Options Aplenty
With countless options to explore, this home and property is a must for the discerning buyer. A rare offering of 600 sqm in the Growth Zone, making it an ideal candidate for future subdivision (stca) with multiple possibilities & designs afforded in this zoning. A solid home that includes a stylishly renovated bathroom, 3 generous bedrooms, updates to the kitchen the home is ready to enjoy. Solid with red bricks, terracotta roof tiles there is a character and charm of a post war era and internally exposed hardwood timber floors are warm and practical. This home is really exudes appeal. Corio Shopping Central (which offers everything) is just a short stroll away as well as schools, transport and a little further along you have the new hospital/wellness centre (under construction) and easy access to the Ring Road or into Geelong Centre itself. With loads of possibilities and opportunities it's what best suits you.
Due Diligence checklist are available at www.consumer.vic.gov.au/duediligencechecklist

Description:
Freshly Renovated Delight!
Situated on a practical corner block this newly renovated 3 bedroom home set on a 628m2 allotment (approx) is ideal for investors looking to take advantage of a savvy investment opportunity or first home buyers looking to get into the market.
Featuring 3 good sized bedrooms 2 with built-in robes, stylish kitchen and meals area that boasts brand new stove with gas cooktop, rangehood, dishwasher, contemporary black sink and plenty of bench and cupboard space, an ample lounge with loads of natural light and heater, new flooring and carpets throughout, plus a central bathroom with shower and bath that easily services the home.
Step out to the neat and secure low maintenance backyard that is easily accessed via a lockable roller door from Torbreck street and you are met by a convenient garage and tidy garden.
This fantastic package located within walking distance to local pre-school, high schools and a short drive to Corio village shopping centre and medical facilities makes this property ideal for young families, first home buyers, investors or downsizers. Easy access to the Geelong Ring Road and Princes Highway also make for an effortless commute.
This property is bound to tick multiple boxes for a multitude of buyers. Make sure this one is on your inspection list.
Key Features
*3 bedrooms
*628m2 corner block (approx)
*New flooring throughout
*New appliances & stylish updated kitchen
*Predicted rental return of $320.00 - $330.00 P/W
*Low maintenance yards
*Short distance to all major amenities
*Every precaution has been taken to establish accuracy of the above information but does not constitute any representation by the vendor or agent.

Description:
Stunning, Sophisticated & Surprisingly Spacious
In the Cloverdale Estate now is the time to enjoy life and make the most it, enjoying what you love to do and not have to do. This better than brand new home will allow you to have the lifestyle you want in a stunning and spacious abode. Crafted by Long Island Homes just over a year ago the dwelling sprawls to almost 18 squares of living consisting of a generous master bedroom with a dazzling en suite and walk-in-robes plus another 2 bedrooms with built-in-robes, the central bathroom is practical and stylish while even the laundry is a show stopper with cupboard & bench space plus loads of light. It's not until you enter the main open living area that you really understand the size of the home. This space consists of a striking kitchen that includes quality 900 mm stove and oven, dishwasher, stone benches and a huge walk-in-pantry and flows to the dining and lounge which can each accommodate groups of friends and with flow to either area which is inviting to entertain and continues to a courtyard. Also features floating timber floors, central heating, reverse cycle split system, double blinds, solar and gas hot water and a water tank plus all delivered in display quality inside and out with a colour palate that is both modern and homely. Handy for anyone wanting easy Ring Road access and with shops, transport and schools not too far away. Love surprises, inspect, you will be impressed.
Due Diligence checklist are available at www.consumer.vic.gov.au/duediligencechecklist

All the hard work has been done for you.
This stunning, newly renovated, residence is proudly positioned in a highly regarded location. Modern tones and a sunny personality are recurring themes throughout this immaculate property. The conveniences of the popular location are enriched by a selection of schooling options all within easy reach to public transport, Corio Shopping Centre and the Princes Highway for commuters. Boasting interior highlights such as the stunning modern kitchen with pantry, dishwasher & gas stove. Renovated to meet the most demanding of needs this home really is the whole package. Be sure to get in quick, an offer this good won't last long!

Set in a quiet Court location tucked away from the hustle and bustle, yet so convenient to everything the Northern Suburbs has to offer. Public transport, local shopping strip & medical facilities all at your fingertips, Corio Shopping Centre only a few minutes drive. With the Ring Road entrance just up the Road, brings easy access to the Surfcoast, Werribee & Melbourne perfect for commuters or the summer family beach trips.
A stunning renovation has recently transformed this property into a home that you can move into with not a thing to do, with the growing family in mind, generous bedrooms all allow plenty of storage with built in robes and the addition of a study nook away from the main living of the home.
-4 large bedrooms all with built in robes
-Central bathroom with oversized shower & separate toilet
-Large open kitchen with stainless steel appliances including 900mm gas cooktop, electric oven & dishwasher + luxurious stone benches
-Large open living area with polished floor boards flowing throughout the home
-Ample off street car parking with long driveway plus double carport & single tandem garage
-Ducted heating & evaporative cooling throughout
-Study nook
-Large concrete patio for entertaining or the carport would be perfect for all weather entertaining
-671 sqm (approx.) block
All the hard work has been done & this move in ready home needs nothing more done to move in an enjoy!

Your Very Own Oasis
Situated on a generous 725m2 block (approx) you'll find this excellent updated home in a quiet court location that is full of beautiful surprises and is sure to impress even the most fastidious of buyers.
Featuring 4 bedrooms 2 with built-in robes, third bedroom with walk-in robe and a spacious master with split system, convenient access to the outdoor entertaining area and tastefully updated en-suite with double vanity and large shower. A light-filled lounge offers a second split system and effortlessly flows through to the fully updated kitchen with stainless steel appliances, 900mm stove and a walk-in pantry/laundry combo, all of which make for a very welcoming and family-friendly central zone.
The exterior of the property is fully equipped with a luxurious solar heated inground pool with water feature, a large Bali hut, undercover alfresco with cafe-style blinds, two outdoor ceiling fans and plenty of rear yard space perfect for entertaining your family or friends.
Extra features include ducted heating throughout, a carport with roller door, 3 split systems throughout, a central bathroom with a spa bath that easily services the home and much more.

Description:
Endless Possibilities!
Set on a generous 655m2 parcel of land and enviably positioned at the gateway to Geelong within close proximity of shops, schools and public transport, this residence presents an array of possibilities! Astute investors and developers will recognise the potential to sub-divide and develop (STCA). Alternatively, renovate or enjoy a passive income when you rent out. Featuring a warm colour scheme throughout, the existing three-bedroom dwelling offers large lounge room with dado-panelled feature wall incorporating in-built gas heater with mantle.
